Form
=======================================================

>> 2 Route use most get and post

Create view file using cmd
>> php artisan make:view ViewName

Laravel Provide a default table "users" -
(database/migations/)

Laravel - Default table - "users"

Difference between GET and POST

GET			
>> Unsecure
>> Pass Data from one page to another
>> Slow

POST
>> Secure
>> Data Save
>> Fast


What is 419 Page Expired Error?

This error comes usually in FOrm.
This error means CSRF token not passed.

CSRF - Cross-site request forgery
-----------------------------------------
To protect your form from Hackers.
It passes a unique token.

To Pass CSRF in FORM - @csrf

-------------------------------------------
FORM Validation
-----------------------------------------
To validate form data, we use Validation.
Rules :-
required - Field is compulsory
min:LENGTH - Specify minimum Length
max:LENGTH - Specify maximum Length
alpha - Only Alphabets are allowed
numeric - Only Digits are allowed


Advance Validation
=========================================

Create our custom validation error message